    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Coarse, strong linen or cotton twill in various weights and with a warp face; used for durable clothing and furnishings.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
